query:
INSERT INTO
            achievements(id, series_id, title, description, jades, hidden)
        VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT
            (id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            series_id = EXCLUDED.series_id,
            title = EXCLUDED.title,
            description = EXCLUDED.description,
            jades = EXCLUDED.jades,
            hidden = EXCLUDED.hidden
